{"tid":1538783,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【策略向/攻略向】我唔撚想輸啊！！！！軟件必須升級（上）","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:37:41.000Z","uid":182843,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c89b1fbf91990c7118d7100d110f4824f254e4d","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"講緊打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點upgrade電腦系統<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae68878039c18db0920b01417511b5ee7615d22e","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. tg洩密/有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題好嚴重，你幾時有見過班狗提前話你知佢會喺邊到佈防？或者佢地今日會放定卧底狗咬你？<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一句講晒，我地唔可以再做節目預告！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所謂兄弟姊妹爬山，各自努力；不分化不篤灰不譴責，我地就要相信大家嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n我建議<span style=\"color: red;\">以後除咗和理非嘅大型吹雞遊行及集會之外，所有會對港共政府產生頗大傷害嘅勇武行動一概都唔set公海gp。</span>真正做嘢嘅話，可以同朋友組隊先（最好認識至少半年或以上，知道對方背景。唔係搞分化，總之各位防人之心一定要有。要組成大gp就frd搭frd，at least大group入面你要有一個超信得過嘅老死。）冇朋友咁慘嘅話就幫做下哨兵，出街鳩嗚鳩行幫其他手足提前探下路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 策略升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n盡量精簡！smh一篇社評啟發到香港人對於和理勇武嘅手段有更進階嘅運用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: green;\">拆燈柱、拆荃灣黑竇、拆黨鐵或者對奶共店鋪做成實際破壞</span><br />\n先係勇武嘅真正用武之地<br />\n並唔係響條街上鬥企對峙<br />\n尤其是最好配合住其他地區有遊行集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />//<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打講得相當有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武點解就一定要同狗同黑社會搏鬥同送頭？<span style=\"color: green;\">真正嘅禾勇不分家，係講緊互相掩護</span>。以大行動日為例，和理非一方面爭取社會注意力，協助分散黑警人力資源。另一方面勇武為和理非製造退路，確保佢地可以全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n而你以為禾勇只限大行動日先會連成一線？錯！呢種禾勇不分家嘅策略係可以延續到去日常生活，成為一種<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">生活態度</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個人都可以禾勇合一，be water be shapeless。大丈夫能屈能伸，隨時準備好做任何一個角色就係無敵！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港已經無太多時間淨，我地唔可以跟支共節奏咁去拖長嚟打場仗。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係仲諗住等選舉啊嘛？靠建制AB隊出賣關鍵一席同香港利益？<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好傻啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>而家唯一可以等嘅都係等美國英國出手，通過<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">《香港人權及民主法案》</span></span>，或者宣佈支共違反《中英聯合聲明》（雖然後者機會不大）<br />\n<br />\n但喺等嘅過程唔能夠坐以待斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一個方法我覺得可以一試嘅，但已經打得太多字，所以之後會再開po<br />\n<br />\n可參考：<br />\n轉貼： 明刀明槍的示威行動會漸漸消失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375656</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35c0d66b03dbce7a5e433275ad2b7079434e4c32","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f43a3ffb172213a0fd2aaac2aefc35eccd3f0362","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"87a0a675a8fda007c58de71f14759e4c21bc0609","tid":1538783,"uid":279650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"到底呢個寫正經野， 但tldr嘅po有冇連登仔推呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d61560238066837297f1c7827dd3934f7f50bce","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"4caa52d02a9d43efdb0d198b3cdd30e2973379d5","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"403d47a4721eec61a891c97b8dcb5226fe435345","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"9614e0dbb23f17867b054c445dcd3c403511a2b8","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"288bcb46b7d12485977291f7ec5b5fc86527459a","tid":1538783,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月7 機場<br />\n9月8 美領</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"d2dffadaa5cb470f39a0217c883285a30b38aaa0","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"48884a2a1683e065c9cf1b3da82deb871a951fe3","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"06e560f16ec3207732c6a5bd829afec0df6b1713","tid":1538783,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:30.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"140591228a805e9516a15b90a2182c88c9c9684f","tid":1538783,"uid":74155,"like":0,"disli